Terms of Service

Last Updated: October 10, 2025

1. Acceptance of Terms

By accessing and using Nestoria Inc.'s services, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.

2. Use of Service

Our service allows you to search, compare, and book hotel accommodations. You agree to:

  • Provide accurate and complete information during registration and booking
  • Maintain the confidentiality of your account credentials
  • Notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account
  • Use the service only for lawful purposes

3. Booking and Payments

When you make a booking through Nestoria Inc.:

  • You enter into a direct contract with the hotel
  • Payment must be made in full at the time of booking
  • All prices are subject to availability and may change without notice
  • Taxes and service charges are clearly indicated before payment

4. Cancellation Policy

Our standard cancellation policy allows:

  • Free cancellation up to 24 hours before check-in
  • No refund for cancellations made within 24 hours of check-in
  • Individual hotels may have different policies, which will be clearly stated
  • Refunds will be processed within 7-10 business days

5. User Responsibilities

As a user, you are responsible for:

  • Arriving at the hotel at the specified check-in time
  • Providing valid identification documents
  • Respecting hotel property and other guests
  • Paying for any damages or additional services not covered in the booking

6. Intellectual Property

All content on the Nestoria Inc. platform, including text, graphics, logos, and software, is the property of Nestoria Inc. or its content suppliers and is protected by copyright laws.

7. Limitation of Liability

Nestoria Inc. acts as an intermediary between customers and hotels. We are not liable for:

  • Quality of services provided by hotels
  • Changes made by hotels to their facilities or policies
  • Force majeure events affecting your stay
  • Personal injuries or property damage during your stay

8. Privacy

Your privacy is important to us. We collect and use your information in accordance with our Privacy Policy. By using our services, you consent to our collection and use of personal data as outlined in our Privacy Policy.

9. Modifications to Terms

Nestoria Inc. reserves the right to modify these terms at any time. We will notify users of significant changes via email or through prominent notices on our platform. Continued use of our services after such modifications constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.

10. Contact Information

For questions or concerns regarding these Terms of Service, please contact us at:

  • Email: legal@nestoria.com
  • Phone: +91 1800-123-4567
  • Address: Nestoria Inc., 123 Business Park, Mumbai, Maharashtra, India
